external_knowledge:
Active plugins refer to plugins that are currently enabled and being used within the application; 
Default views are the views that are automatically selected for users unless they choose otherwise;
Cumulative counts represent the running totals of these metrics across all users in the order they are listed.

sql:
SELECT sort_method_name, sort_method_description
FROM sort_methods
WHERE is_default = 0 AND last_updated LIKE '2023%';
